Class BulkTranformContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aurel.track.fieldType.bulkSetters.BulkTranformContext

  • public class BulkTranformContext
extends java.lang.Object
    A transormation context for transforming the bulk values to workItemBean attributes Typically they are the same (SET_TO) but for some relations a transformation is needed (SET_EARLIEST_STARTING_FROM, MOVE_BY_DAYS, ADD_IF_SET)
